// Clockwise from top: MedSci(N) → Provider(NE) → Patient(SE) → PubHealth(S)
//                   → HealthTech(SW) → Policy(W) → Payer(NW)
// Hub at (0,0). Ring-1 moat {(1,0),(-1,0),(0,1),(0,-1),(1,-1),(-1,1)} is empty.
const ZONE_DEFS = [

