      {q:4,  r:-5, type:'node',    label:'Predictive\nAnalytics',  nodeId:'predictive',
        desc:'Sepsis prediction, readmission risk, no-show models. Most clinical AI in production is here. Calibration drift and alert fatigue are the primary failure modes.',
